Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.63,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}無謀な挑戦者さ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:33.84,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:13.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}手にした刃で明日を切り開けばいいんだろ
