Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:33.84,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:25.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}cause we are still rough diamonds on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:02.10,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}堰きを切た喉から手がでるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:03.94,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しいぐなだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:07.67,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕じゃない　別の誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:12.82,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夢と希望　他に何がいると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:18.07,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思えだ頃の僕は今いつーごえ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:20.72,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}長い物に巻がれで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:23.33,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失った道しるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:25.97,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生ど死の狭間にわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:28.97,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}スノードロップが咲き乱れる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:31.42,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何かの間違いで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:34.45,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}砕け散ってしまったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:39.58,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}せめで僕の抜け殻に　花束を添えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:45.00,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなもんかな　こんなもんでしょう　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.33,0:23:50.31,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あきらめだと思われたって構わないけど　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:56.02,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らしくない　僕らしくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:24:00.67,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}誰にだて作れもんに価値はない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:28.54,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}比心中描繪的意象更遙遠的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:34.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}在一筆筆敘寫  那真實還在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.85,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}如無盡的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:43.89,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}來將各自的自尊心研磨透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:48.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}敞開任何言語之類的裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:58.32,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相互碰撞 相互摩擦 rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.99,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相遇是 shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:06.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}向未知的世界邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.63,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}無謀的挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:13.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}只要用手中的刀劈開明天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:16.05,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}這並不是別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:19.85,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}是只屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:25.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}因為我們都是未經琢磨的鑽石！
